#: ../../docs/classes/class_particlesmaterial.rst:14
msgid ""
"Particle properties for :ref:`Particles <class_Particles>` and "
":ref:`Particles2D <class_Particles2D>` nodes."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Particles <class_Particles>` 和 :ref:`Particles2D "
