#: ../../docs/classes/class_particlesmaterial.rst:17
msgid "Description"
msgstr "说明"

#: ../../docs/classes/class_particlesmaterial.rst:19
msgid ""
"ParticlesMaterial defines particle properties and behavior. It is used in"
" the ``process_material`` of :ref:`Particles <class_Particles>` and "
":ref:`Particles2D <class_Particles2D>` emitter nodes."
msgstr ""
"粒子材质定义粒子属性和行为。它在 :ref:`Particles <class_Particles>` 和 :ref:`Particles2D "
"<class_Particles2D>` 发射器节点的 ``process_material`` 中使用。"

#: ../../docs/classes/class_particlesmaterial.rst:21
msgid ""
"Some of this material's properties are applied to each particle when "
"emitted, while others can have a :ref:`CurveTexture <class_CurveTexture>`"
" applied to vary values over the lifetime of the particle."
msgstr ""
"该材质的某些属性在发射时，会应用于每个粒子，而其他属性可以应用一个 :ref:`CurveTexture "
"<class_CurveTexture>`，来在粒子的整个生命周期内改变值。"

#: ../../docs/classes/class_particlesmaterial.rst:23
msgid ""
"When a randomness ratio is applied to a property it is used to scale that"
" property by a random amount. The random ratio is used to interpolate "
"between ``1.0`` and a random number less than one, the result is "
"multiplied by the property to obtain the randomized property. For example"
" a random ratio of ``0.4`` would scale the original property between "
"``0.4-1.0`` of its original value."
msgstr ""
"当将随机率应用于属性时，它将按随机量缩放该属性。随机率用于在 ``1.0`` "
"和一个小于1的随机数之间进行插值，将结果乘以该属性以获得随机属性。例如，``0.4`` 的随机率将使原始属性，缩放到原始值的 "
"``0.4-1.0`` 之间。"

